issue.title: gazebo7 not working with gzweb branch upgrade-node

content.raw:
can you open the browser's developer console in the browser and see what are errors printed?  Were you able to run other worlds?

I was able to launch rubble.world in `upgrade-node` and `default` branch. I suggest using the `default` branch.
